            "type": "text",
            "text": "Brand Personality"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "VidRevamp is the tireless editor who never sleeps. Fast, efficient, and obsessively optimized for the creator economy. The brand feels tech-forward but creator-first \u2014 built by someone who understands the grind, not a faceless software company."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "level": 2,
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Voice & Tone"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "unordered-list",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "list-item",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Energetic and punchy \u2014 mirrors the short-form content it creates"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "list-item",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Results-focused \u2014 features are always framed in terms of views and growth"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "list-item",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Conversational \u2014 talks like a creator, not a SaaS product manager"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
